e): align help headers with theme layout\r\n* Select Music menu: add **Practice Mode** entry + navigation to `ScreenPractice`\r\n* Player Options: exit flow respects Practice return (start Practice / ΓÇ£choose differentΓÇ¥ returns to Select Music)\r\n\r\n### Options / UI polish\r\n* fix(options): measure cursor ring with translated Exit label\r\n* feat(options): accelerate Max FPS adjustment (1 FPS steps + hold-to-accelerate behavior)\r\n\r\n### Input / focus handling\r\n* fix(input): drop background keystrokes when window is unfocused (#276)\r\n* App: seed focus on window show + explicitly mark unfocused during backend teardown/reinit\r\n\r\n### Gameplay / visuals\r\n* fix(gameplay): keep pack banner edge alignment doubles-only\r\n* Gameplay/Notefield: large internal update supporting Practice screen integration\r\n\r\n### Performance\r\n* perf(compose): remove dynamic frame texture pointer maps\r\n* perf(compose): reuse scratch buffers for mask clipping\r\n* perf(audio): drain playback map under one lock\r\n* perf(video): recycle discarded frame buffers\r\n* perf(video): skip queued frames while upload is pending\r\n* Assets: expose `has_pending_texture_upload` and gate video frame dequeue/upload when a texture upload is already pending\r\n\r\n### Timing / simfiles\r\n* simfiles: bump song cache version and cache time signatures\r\n* timing: add time signature segments + default 4/4 fallback when missing\r\n\r\n### Dependencies / maintenance\r\n* chore(deps): update coreaudio-rs to v0.14.2\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/pnn64/deadsync/compare/v0.3.858...v0.3.871\n\n## What's Changed\n* Fix Options cursor highlight bounds after language change by @adstep in https://github.com/pnn64/deadsync/pull/296\n* fix(input): drop background keystrokes when window is unfocused (#276) by @adstep in https://github.com/pnn64/deadsync/pull/298\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/pnn64/deadsync/compare/v0.3.858...v0.3.871","mentions_count":1}
